ivers: low-visibility procedures (reduced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) and 3 others. Changed since last run: Malmö Sturup (MMX/ESMS), Lennart Meri Tallinn (TLL/EETN), Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO), Göteborg Landvetter (GOT/ESGG), Suceava Stefan cel Mare (SCV/LRSV), Craiova (CRA/LRCV), Stockholm Skavsta (NYO/ESKN), Stockholm-Arlanda (ARN/ESSA), Bacău George Enescu (BCM/LRBC), Plovdiv (PDV/LBPD) and 2 others.",
